Ekh '''lakh''' ([[Bangla]]: লাখ) si ekh gin le [[Desi ginavipnasko sistem]]osko prinjardo kai [[Bharat]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Pakistan]], [[Shri Lanka]], [[Myanmar]]. Ekh lakh si [[100000|ekh shel miye]] (10<sup>5</sup>). Ekh shel lakh si ekh [[kror]] vai desh miliyonurya.

Kadava ginavipen thol xulavitorya pe aver thana sar avryal i [[Sudutni Asiya]]. Sar misalyake, 30 lakh (3 miliyonurya) lekhavdyovel sar 30,00,000 chi 3,000,000.

Kadava gin si vi andi [[Svahili chhib]], navyardo ''lakhi''. Pe chorengi chhib andar [[Mumbai]] phenel pes ''peti''.

Kai [[Gaudiya Vaishnava|Bangla Vaishnava]] ekh lakh si o divesutno acharuno bashavipen le [[Hari|Hareske]] nava [http://wiki.gaudiyakutir.com/Lakh]; le duma ''ekh lakh nava'' janglyoven but.

